				<font face="verdana" size="2"><Blockquote>

<B><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/036843.html">I'm betting the "name nazis" on Vallon Zek are doing it just to get a rise</a></B><P>

I'm betting the "name nazis" on Vallon Zek are doing it just to get a rise out of people and then sit back and watch the message boards overflow with complaints. I'd bet verant's profits that they are sitting back and chuckling and joking with each other about it right now, guides, guide managers, Abashi, Absor, etc alike.<P>

<B>Ok everyone, enough.<P>

Let's stop using 'nazi' to describe anyone here. It's a very offensive choice of terminology. Consider doing so worthy of a warning from here on out. I have no problem with people talking about our policies, even if you don't like them. But using terminology that is designed only to offend people like this is something that I'm not going to allow.<P>

Alan</B><P>

<HR align="center" width="75%"><P>

