<HR align="center" width="75%"><P>

<B><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/036913.html">Full Screen looting/inspecting: Why isn't that free?</a></B><P>

ProppaT wrote: "My only gripe is that it's not new content...it's a fix to a bug."<P>

<B>No, it's new content. The old interface wasn't bugged. In fact, a lot of the changes that we've made and simply added to the game were improvements to the interface, not bug fixes. Is it better? Absolutely. Is it a bug fix, no.<P>

Alan</B><P>

<HR align="center" width="75%"><P>

