Week 2's item prices contest winners have been choosen.<P>

Our top entry was Benlron The Great with a total of 279 price's submitted.<P>

And our three lucky random winners are:<BR>
Arie<BR>
wizman<BR>
Quartx<P>

The above mentioned people all win an Everlore T-Shirt. If you're curious how you can win, here's how to participate: Each week, we will choose four winners. Three people that have submitted item prices during that week will be chosen randomly and one person will be chosen that has the most item price submissions for that week. Remember, you can only win once the entire contest. So head on over to our <a href="http://www.everlore.com/items/">Items Page</a> and start giving us your accurate price details.<P>

This contest lasts for the next two weeks as we continue to give away prizes. Lastly our congratulations go out to all the winners, and our thanks to everyone that submitted a price this week.
