Tonight on Solusek Ro at about 3:30 AM Est, three brownies appeared in Faymart. Their leader, Bubba Thornbush, shouted something about having come to reclaim their homeland. Immediately shouts of "Kill them!!!" Rang out. I disagreed and quickly shouted to form a party to go parley with them.<P>

Well, we grouped up and ran up the the brownies to parley. Unfortunately, they didn't like my having organized my little group, and all three proceeded to pound on me. Fortunately, they were pansies to me at lvl 30. I tried for 2 minutes to get them to cease their agressions and parley before I had had enough. We forthwith and with extreme prejudice dispatched them.<P>

They looted extremely lousy, dropping a FS weapon each, no money, and together 2 glowing wooden crooks and a ice crystal staff. To make it worse no GM showed up afterwards to hand out goodies. (Fat lotta good me vocally organizing the group to parley did :)<P>

Overall if kinda stunk, but was cool not to die in my first ever GM event.<P>

